'''''Rarely Affectionate (I)''''' is a [[Companion Mission]] in the chapter [[Slices of Life Before the Furnace]].

==Steps==
# Ask Clara about the trouble in the Robot Settlement
# Question the witness of the theft cases involving mechanical parts
# Search for clues regarding the culprit
# Follow the clues and search onward
# Continue to look for clues of the culprit
# Find the source of the odd sounds
# Follow Clara back to Svarog's base
# Find Toby near the gates of the base
# Follow Toby
# Keep following Toby
# Report back to Clara

